2013-07-10  Alejandro Gallardo <alejandro.gallardo@artica.es>
	
	* index.php: Some changes on pdf output.
	
	* integria_db.sql: Table 'tinvoice' updated. "ammount" column
	replaced for "amount1", "amount2", "amount3", "amount4",
	"amount5" columns. Added "concept1", "concept2", "concept3",
	"concept4", "concept5" columns. "bill_id" has now an int type.
	"invoice_create_date" and "invoice_payment_date" has now date
	type.
	
	* extras/migrate.sql: Added the changes of 'tinvoice';
	  
	* include/functions_crm.php: Function "crm_change_invoice_lock"
	now works properly.
	
