	and "get_invoice_amount" fixed with the amount changes.
	
	* include/functions_tasks.php: Function "task_cost_invoices"
	fixed with the amount changes.
	
	* include/pdf_translator.php: Now is possible to set the entire
	html code of the footer of the pdf output.
	
	* include/ajax/remote_validations.php: Added a new check in
	"search_existing_invoice". Now search if the "bill_id" is
	larger or smaller than the larger "bill_id" in the database.
	
	* operation/companies/company_detail.php: Now an invoice can
	be locked in the invoices section of the company. Now the
	invoices listing shows the new invoices options.
	
	* operation/invoices/invoice_detail.php: Fixed an error related
	to delete an invoice with a non existant id. Added a link
	to the company of every invoice in the invoice section.
	
	* operation/invoices/invoice_template.php: Finished the
	invoice template.
	
	* operation/invoices/invoice_view.php: Little fixes. Added ACL.
	
	* operation/invoices/invoices.php: Now shows a read version
	of the invoice if it is locked. Fixed the create and update of
	an invoice with the changes of the table 'tinvoice'. Now an
	invoice can be locked or deleted from its edit or read view.
	Changed the invoices form. Added new rules of validation to
	"bill_id", "tax" and the amount columns.

