2013-04-07  Sancho Lerena <slerena@artica.es>

	* operation/companies/company_detail.php: Show only active leads, sorted
	by estimated sale.

	* operation/workorders/wo.php: Fixed ACL check on admins. Added
	search parameters to delete link for usability.

	* operation/leads/lead_detail.php: Improved main view, now can delete 
	or close from the list, for better operation.

	* extras/migrate.sql: Updated more SQL for 3.1 to 4.0 migration.

	* general/header.php: Better style.

	* general/home.php: Fixes issues on agenda -> workorder, and also fixed 
	problems with agenda items.

	* godmode/usuarios/lista_usuarios.php: Last conection time is better shown.

	* images/ack.png
	images/ack_bn.png
	images/wo_category: New icons.

	* include/ajax/users.php: Improved regexp to search on ANY position of the 
	substring.

	* include/functions_calendar.php: Try to improve the SQL queries on month
	calendar, but doesnt seem to improve much :(

	* include/functions_config.php: Removed "agenda" from menu visibility array.

	* include/functions_db.php: todos_active_user() now returns active WO before
	return all. Fixed get_project_manager_users() to return only users which are
	under a user witch is project manager.

	* include/functions_form.php: Added translate_wo_status() and wo_status_array().

	* include/functions_graph.php: Added border/mark on specific graph to see better
	in layout (this is a specific fix for task detail page).

	* include/styles/integria.css: Minor changes in styles for main menu and header.

	* integria_db.sql: Added company and todo on tattachment, tcompany has now
	manager, parent, website and country, new fields on ttodo to implement the 
	workorder new features, new bits on tprofile for CRM and File Releases.

	* operation/companies/company_detail.php: Added new fields and remove old ones to
	company management, improved listing.

	* operation/companies/company_export.php: Added CSV export to company listing.

	* operation/companies/company_files.php: Added file attach to company management.

	* operation/contracts/contract_detail.php: Removed group issues in contracts. No
	more ACL's based on contracts here. TODO: implement proper ACL management based
	on company relationship.

	* operation/leads/lead_detail.php,
	operation/leads/lead_files.php: Several fixes and adjustments.
	
	* operation/leads/lead_forward.php: new feature to send lead details by mail.

	* operation/main_menu.php: New layout for main menu.

	* operation/projects/csvexport.php: Delete unused report file.

	* operation/projects/project.php: Listing show now project manager.

	* operation/projects/project_detail.php: Fixed some value calculation.

	* operation/projects/task.php: Removed some info from listing.

	* operation/projects/task_detail.php: Small hack to have a better pie graph
	layout (with a frame around).

	* operation/side_menu.php: Fixed missing enterprise profile management, fixed
	missing agenda and other new options added and some (taskcsv) removed.

	* operation/user_report/monthly.php,
	operation/user_report/report_annual.php,
	operation/user_report/report_full.php,
	operation/user_report/report_monthly.php: Fixed lots of ACL's problems. Fixed
	some form issues also.

	* operation/workorders,
	operation/workorders/wo.php,
	operation/workorders/wo_category.php,
	operation/workorders/wo_files.php: Rewrite from scratch: new Workorder feature.
	This will replace "todo's". Implements also a new category for todos, proper file
	management attached to todos, todos ACL's and much more features.

