	* images/icon_lead.png: New icon for lead.

	* include/api.php: Upgraded the api to support lead creation from api.

	* include/integria_cron.php: Mail now uses optional from.

	* include/functions_form.php: Added progress step (Invalid) on leads.

	* include/functions_config.php: Added new token: Lead warning time.

	* include/functions_calendar.php: Added new function: calendar_time_diff 
	to show seconds passed from a given date.

	* include/functions.php: integria_sendmail() now supports optional
	parameter to do not include "global" header/footer and also an optional
	parameter to define a different "from" address.

	* include/styles/integria.css: New styles.

	* operation/side_menu.php: New menu entries for lead management.

	* integria_db.sql, 
	integria_dbdata.sql: Upgraded SQL code.

	* operation/companies/company_detail.php: Delete a company from the from.

	* godmode/setup/logviewer.php: Improved view.

	Some of this code has been merged from 3.1 branch. Has been tested and it works 100%.

