	in the RCPT field :-S... now is fixed by using a prober trim with
	safe output function (was not working due the encoding).

	* functions_api.php: Added api_get_stats().

	* api.php: Added get_stats() method, and fixed the way on how the
	include is loaded. Always uses absolute path load to avoid security
	problems!.

