	* include/functions.php: Added function to render numbers with units.

	* operation/incidents/incident_download_file.php: Directly do a 
	header redirect to file. This avoid problems with huge files.

	* operation/download/download.php: Huge files (>80MB) are always
	downloaded using a HTTP header redirection, smaller files are buffered
	(Session close before, to avoid app. locking) and tiny files are 
	not buffered (< 256KB).

